---
title: Chimichurri Burgers with Avocado, Monterey Jack, and Cabbage Slaw
description: Chimichurri—an Argentine herb sauce—is one of the most flavorful condiments out there. We’re making it with parsley, lemon, and garlic for a kick. Its brightness cuts through the burger’s intense richness. Cubed avocado lends this side slaw a little extra creaminess.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chimichurri-burgers-93cd8603.jpg
